           .withColumn('doy_s', udf_scaler_doy('day_of_year'))\

def create_model2(layers, nodes, drop_pr):
    model = Sequential()
    
    model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform', input_dim=3))
    model.add(Activation('relu'))
    model.add(Dropout(drop_pr))
    
    for i in range(2, layers):
        model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform'))
        model.add(Activation('relu'))
        model.add(Dropout(drop_pr))

    model.add(Dense(1))
    model.compile(optimizer='adam', loss='mape', metrics=['mse'])

    return model

%pyspark

def create_model3(layers, nodes, drop, opt):
    model = Sequential()
    
    model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform', input_dim=3))
    model.add(Activation('relu'))
    model.add(Dropout(drop))
    
    for i in range(2, layers):
        model.add(Dense(nodes, kernel_initializer='random_uniform'))
        model.add(Activation('relu'))
        model.add(Dropout(drop))

    model.add(Dense(1))
    model.compile(optimizer=opt, loss='mape', metrics=['mse'])

    return model

%pyspark
udf_10min = udf(lambda t: t[:4] + '0', StringType())

realdata = spdf.where('date = "2019-09-18"')\
               .select('time', 'illum', 'illum_s', 'solar_zenith', 'sz_s',
                       'day_of_year', 'doy_s', 'uvi').sort('time')
pdf_realdata = realdata.toPandas()

input = pdf_realdata.to_numpy()
# print(input[:10])
# print(input[:10, [2, 4, 6]])

output = pd.DataFrame(model.predict(input[:, [2, 4, 6]]), columns=['uvi_predic'])

pdf_real_result = pdf_realdata[['time', 'uvi']]
pdf_real_result['uvi_predic'] = output['uvi_predic']
# print(pdf_real_result)

spdf_real_result = spark.createDataFrame(pdf_real_result)

spdf_real_result2 = spdf_real_result.withColumn('time_min', udf_10min('time'))\
                        .groupby('time_min').avg('uvi', 'uvi_predic').sort('time_min')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi)', 'uvi')\
                        .withColumnRenamed('avg(uvi_predic)', 'uvi_predic')

spdf_real_result2.show()
spdf_real_result2.createOrReplaceTempView('real_result')
